BULLET::::- &lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;. "&lt;a href="http%3A//abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory%3Fid%3D2139151"&gt;Man Sues Over Web Site Comments&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AABC%20News"&gt;ABC News&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 30, 2006
