BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2006/WORLD/asiapcf/07/01/japan.hashimoto.reut/index.html"&gt;Outspoken Japanese former PM dies&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 1, 2006
