BULLET::::- Robert H. Reid. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.suntimes.com/output/iraq/cst-nws-iraq02s1.html"&gt;Car bomb kills 66 in Shiite district&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AChicago%20Sun-Times"&gt;Chicago Sun-Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 2, 2006
