BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//today.reuters.com/news/newsarticle.aspx%3Ftype%3DtopNews%26amp%3Bstoryid%3D2006-07-04T010000Z_01_N01351649_RTRUKOC_0_US-SPACE-SHUTTLE.xml%26amp%3Bsrc%3Drss"&gt;NASA to launch space shuttle despite foam crack&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 3, 2006

