BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.swissinfo.org/eng/top_news/detail/Swiss_urge_Israel_to_respect_humanitarian_law.html%3FsiteSect%3D106%26amp%3Bsid%3D6867521%26amp%3BcKey%3D1151995514000"&gt;Swiss urge Israel to respect humanitarian law&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ASwissinfo"&gt;Swissinfo&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 3 2006

</ul>


