<ul>
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="World%27s%20highest%20railway%20links%20Tibet%20to%20rest%20of%20China"&gt;World's highest railway links Tibet to rest of China&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="Main_Page"&gt;Wikinews&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt;, July 1, 2006
<h2>Sources</h2>
