BULLET::::- Diário Digital / Lusa. "&lt;a href="http%3A//diariodigital.sapo.pt/news.asp%3Fsection_id%3D13%26amp%3Bid_news%3D235213"&gt;IPPAR cancela exumação de D.Afonso Henriques (act.)&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ADi%C3%A1rio%20Digital"&gt;Diário Digital&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 6, 2006
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//tsf.sapo.pt/online/ciencia/interior.asp%3Fid_artigo%3DTSF172154"&gt;Ministério da Cultura suspende abertura de túmulo&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ATSF%20Online"&gt;TSF Online&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 6, 2006
