BULLET::::- Krittivas Mukherjee, ♡❤&lt;a href="http%3A//today.reuters.co.uk/news/newsArticle.aspx%3Ftype%3DoddlyEnoughNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D2006-07-07T105402Z_01_SP148141_RTRIDST_0_OUKOE-UK-INDIA-PRINCE.XML"&gt;Indian gay prince out of closet, loses inheritance&lt;/a&gt;♡❤, &lt;a href="Reuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;, July 7, 2005.
BULLET::::- Peter Foster, ♡❤&lt;a href="http%3A//www.telegraph.co.uk/news/main.jhtml%3Fxml%3D/news/2006/06/28/wprince28.xml%26amp%3BsSheet%3D/news/2006/06/28/ixnews.html"&gt;Gay prince is cut off from fortune 'for dishonouring his family'&lt;/a&gt;♡❤, Telegraph, June 28, 2006.
BULLET::::- ♡❤&lt;a href="http%3A//story.malaysiasun.com/p.x/ct/9/cid/b8de8e630faf3631/id/28082662bf97c43f/"&gt;Maharajah disinherits gay son&lt;/a&gt;♡❤, Big News Network, July 7, 2006.
