BULLET::::- Jonathan Oliver. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.dailymail.co.uk/pages/live/articles/news/news.html%3Fin_article_id%3D394742%26amp%3Bin_page_id%3D1770"&gt;Now Cameron says: We must love hoodies&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Mail%20on%20Sunday"&gt;The Mail on Sunday&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 9, 2006
