BULLET::::- Lori Culbert. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.canada.com/story.html%3Fid%3D3d49932a-5919-456b-aa67-502bc1c0c9fd%26amp%3Bk%3D77449"&gt;Pickton pig-farm searchers counselled&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AVancouver%20Sun"&gt;Vancouver Sun&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 10,2006

</ul>
