BULLET::::- Katy Byron, Allan Chernoff, Delia Gallagher, Cheryl Bronson. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.cnn.com/2006/US/07/10/building.collapse/index.html"&gt;New York building collapse injures 15&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ACNN"&gt;CNN&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 10
