BULLET::::- Joan Gralla. "&lt;a href="http%3A//today.reuters.co.uk/news/newsArticle.aspx%3Ftype%3DtopNews%26amp%3BstoryID%3D2006-07-10T231428Z_01_N10334591_RTRUKOC_0_UK-USA-EXPLOSION.xml"&gt;NY building collapses after apparent suicide bid&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 10

