<h2>Sources</h2>
<ul>
BULLET::::- Stuff.co.nz. "&lt;a href="http%3A//stuff.co.nz/stuff/0%2C2106%2C3729758a10%2C00.html"&gt;Arrest in Red Rocks murder case&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3Astuff.co.nz"&gt;stuff.co.nz&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 12, 2006

</ul>
&lt;br style="clear:both;"&gt;


