BULLET::::- Schuster C; Kleber H; Snyder S; Nichols D; de Wit H.. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.hopkinsmedicine.org/Press_releases/2006/GriffithsCommentaries.pdf"&gt;Commentaries and Editorial on Article by Griffiths et al.&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3APsychopharmacology%20%28online%20edition%29"&gt;Psychopharmacology (online edition)&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 11, 2006
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.hopkinsmedicine.org/Press_releases/2006/07_11_06.html"&gt;Hopkins Scientists Show Hallucinogen in Mushrooms Creates Universal 'Mystical' Experience&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AJohns%20Hopkins%20Medicine%20news%20release"&gt;Johns Hopkins Medicine news release&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 11, 2006
