BULLET::::- Michael Smith. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.medpagetoday.com/Psychiatry/GeneralPsychiatry/tb/3721"&gt;Psilocybin Viewed as Therapy or Research Tool&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AMedpagetoday.com"&gt;Medpagetoday.com&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 11, 2006
BULLET::::- Roxanne Khamsi. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.newscientist.com/article/dn9522-magic-mushrooms-really-cause-spiritual-experiences.html"&gt;Magic mushrooms really cause 'spiritual' experiences&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANew%20Scientist"&gt;New Scientist&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 11, 2006
BULLET::::- David Brown. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/07/10/AR2006071001304.html"&gt;Drug's Mystical Properties Confirmed&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWashington%20Post"&gt;Washington Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 11, 2006
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/aponline/us/AP-Psychedelic-Research.html"&gt;Mushroom Drug Produces Mystical Experience&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AAssociated%20Press"&gt;Associated Press&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 11, 2006
BULLET::::- Denise Gellene. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.latimes.com/news/science/la-sci-mystical11jul11%2C0%2C3028620.story%3Fcoll%3Dla-home-headlines"&gt;Counterculture Drug Provides Spiritual Boost&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ALos%20Angeles%20Times"&gt;Los Angeles Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 11, 2006
