BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="President%20Bush%20of%20the%20United%20States%20authorized%20NSA%20surveillance%20of%20citizens%2C%20bypassing%20court%20warrants"&gt;President Bush of the United States authorized NSA surveillance of citizens, bypassing court warrants&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="Main_Page"&gt;Wikinews&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt;, December 16, 2005

