BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="North%20Korea%20to%20test%20missile%20that%20could%20reach%20U.S.%20mainland"&gt;North Korea to test missile that could reach U.S. mainland&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="Main_Page"&gt;Wikinews&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt;, June 14, 2006
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="North%20Korea%20fires%20missiles%20during%20training%20exercise"&gt;North Korea fires missiles during training exercise&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="Main_Page"&gt;Wikinews&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt;, March 9, 2006

</ul>
