BULLET::::- Sam F. Ghattas, AP. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/07/16/AR2006071600521.html"&gt;8 Canadians Killed in Israeli Airstrike&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AWashington%20Post"&gt;Washington Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, Sunday, July 16, 2006; 5:54 PM
