BULLET::::- Lin Noueihed. "&lt;a href="http%3A//news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20060717/ts_nm/mideast_dc_395"&gt;Israeli air strikes on Lebanon kill 42 people&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AReuters"&gt;Reuters&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 17, 2006
