BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.nytimes.com/2006/07/19/world/europe/19italy.html%3F_r%3D1%26amp%3Boref%3Dslogin"&gt;Italian Police Free 113 Poles Living in Slave Labor Camps (English)&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ANew%20York%20Times"&gt;New York Times&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 19, 2006
