BULLET::::- Volt Contreras, Tarra V. Quismundo. "&lt;a href="http%3A//specials.inq7.net/thesubicrapecase/index.php%3Fver%3D0%26amp%3Bindex%3D1%26amp%3Bstory_id%3D77903"&gt;Nicole relives ordeal&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3APhilippines%20Inquirer"&gt;Philippines Inquirer&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, June 3, 2006

</ul>

