BULLET::::- Jim Salter. "&lt;a href="http%3A//abcnews.go.com/US/wireStory%3Fid%3D2219645%26amp%3Bpage%3D2"&gt;Guard to St. Louis; Heat Deaths Rise&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AABC"&gt;ABC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, 21 July 2006
