BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.bloomberg.com/apps/news%3Fpid%3D20601084%26amp%3Bsid%3DaHRpF8C20H58%26amp%3Brefer%3Dstocks"&gt;U.S. Stock-Index Futures Gain; Microsoft, Google Advance&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3ABloomberg%20LP"&gt;Bloomberg LP&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 21, 2006
