BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="Indonesia%27s%20president%20visits%20victims%20of%20tsunami"&gt;Indonesia's president visits victims of tsunami&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;a href="Main_Page"&gt;Wikinews&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt;, July 22 2006

</ul>
