BULLET::::- Caryle Murphy. "&lt;a href="http%3A//www.washingtonpost.com/wp-dyn/content/article/2006/07/23/AR2006072300515.html"&gt;Worshipers Hear Call For Middle East Peace&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AThe%20Washington%20Post"&gt;The Washington Post&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 23, 2006
BULLET::::- "&lt;a href="http%3A//msnbc.msn.com/id/13996428/"&gt;Pope prays for peace in 'destroyed' Lebanon&lt;/a&gt;" — &lt;i&gt;&lt;span class="interwiki-link-foreign"&gt;&lt;a href="w%3AMSNBC"&gt;MSNBC&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;/i&gt;, July 23, 2006

</ul>
